creator: Smart Scanner
descriptionHtml:
QR Code/Barcode Scanner is the most lightweight QR & Barcode scanner app for Android you could ever find on Google Play Store and is essential for every android device. It’s not only limited to scanning but you can also use it to create your own code.

QR Code/Barcode Scanner is extremely easy to use. To scan any QR or Barcode simply open the application and align the code. QR Code & Barcode Scanner app will automatically recognize any QR Code or Barcode and provide you only the relevant options for individual QR or Barcode type to take appropriate action.

Key Features of QR Code/Barcode Scanner:

✔️ Scan all types of QR Code and Barcode.
✔️ Flashlight supported for low-light environments.
✔️ History auto saved for all created or scanned QR Code and Barcode.
✔️ Simple and easy to use interface.
✔️ Generate different type of QR Code and Barcode.
✔️ Batch scan mode.
✔️ Scan and share codes with your friends.
✔️ Scan image from Gallery.
✔️ No Internet connection required.
✔️ Export/Import data (CSV file) for created or scanned QR Code and Barcodes.

QR Code/Barcode Scanner app can scan and read all common types of QR Code including text, URL, product, contact, ISBN, calendar, email, location, Wi-Fi and many other formats.

QR Code/Barcode Scanner app also support the functionality of a QR code generator. Using QR generator is extremely easy to use, just enter the data by selecting the appropriate code type and hit the create button to generate the code.

With barcode reader app you can also scan product barcodes. Scan with bar code reader in shops and compare prices with online prices to save money. QR Code/Barcode Scanner app is the only free QR code reader / barcode scanner you will ever need.

We need your constant support to make the QR Code/Barcode Scanner app better with more advanced and exciting features. Please feel free to send us your queries/suggestions/feedback on qrscannerteam@gmail.com. We would love to hear from you.

Upgrade to PRO (NO ADS) version of the app: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.barcode.qrcode.scanner.reader.pro
